nhc_headline: ...OCTAVE MOVING SLOWLY NORTHWESTWARD OVER THE TROPICAL EASTERN PACIFIC...
summary: ...OCTAVE MOVING SLOWLY NORTHWESTWARD OVER THE TROPICAL EASTERN PACIFIC... As of 8:00 AM PDT Wed Oct 01 the center of Octave was located near 11.6, -115.7 with movement NW at 8 mph. The minimum central pressure was 994 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 65 mph.
